{
  "texts": [
    "This study provides valuable insight into the ability of GPT-4 to generate APA-style psychology papers.",
    "While GPT-4 demonstrated potential, it requires improvements in its citation and substantiation abilities, factual accuracy, and adherence to APA-style guidelines.",
    "Addressing these limitations will be crucial in harnessing the full potential of AI language models for scientific writing in psychology, facilitating the work of psychology professionals and upholding the standards of academic rigor and integrity.",
    "Further research and development efforts are needed to refine AI language models and address these limitations.",
    "The continuous evolution of AI, such as the release of GPT-4, calls for ongoing evaluation and adaptation."
  ]
}